---
// Work/System Stories Page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="System Stories · Real Problems, Systematic Solutions">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.441rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          System Stories
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          Real problems, systematic solutions, documented outcomes.
        </p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
          <!-- System Story Card 1 -->
          <div style="padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.563rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Replacing Manual Reporting with Internal Dashboard
            </h3>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Dashboard
              </span>
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Automation
              </span>
            </div>
            <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              A founder was manually reconciling data from 5 spreadsheets every morning to prepare daily reports for the team. The process took 4 hours daily and was error-prone.
            </p>
            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.5); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Outcome</div>
              <div style="font-weight: 600;">Daily reporting time reduced from 4 hours to 10 minutes</div>
            </div>
            <a href="/work/replacing-manual-reporting" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 500;">Read Full Story →</a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- System Story Card 2 -->
          <div style="padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.563rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Automating Client Onboarding Workflows
            </h3>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Workflow Automation
              </span>
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Backend System
              </span>
            </div>
            <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              A service business was using 4 different tools for client onboarding, causing missed steps and inconsistent client experiences.
            </p>
            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.5); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Outcome</div>
              <div style="font-weight: 600;">Onboarding time reduced by 70%, error rate to 0%</div>
            </div>
            <a href="/work/automating-onboarding" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 500;">Read Full Story →</a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- System Story Card 3 -->
          <div style="padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.563rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
              Centralizing Operations Data for Decision Making
            </h3>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Data Integration
              </span>
              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: var(--color-accent); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                Internal Tools
              </span>
            </div>
            <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              A growing company had operational data spread across 8 different tools, making it impossible to get a complete picture of business health.
            </p>
            <div style="padding: 1rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.5); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Outcome</div>
              <div style="font-weight: 600;">Unified view of operations, decision time reduced by 80%</div>
            </div>
            <a href="/work/centralizing-operations-data" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 500;">Read Full Story →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="padding: 3rem; background: var(--color-bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.563rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Have a similar challenge?
          </h3>
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            These systems started with a conversation about a specific operational problem.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Describe Your System Challenge</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
